Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveNigerian man, Kunle Adeyanju, who rode a bike from London to Lagos, has put the bike, Eagle, up for auction.
He announced the auction on Twitter on Wednesday, stating that the opening bid starts from $25,000.
Adeyanju had travelled across the continents to raise awareness for polio.
He said part of the proceeds from the auction will be going towards charity.
